        lessons_learned: "If starting over, we would formalize the selection, equity, and partner-engagement frameworks earlier to better manage scale and set consistent expectations as demand grew. We would also build longitudinal data tracking and evaluation mechanisms into the pilot from the outset to capture longer-term outcomes such as employment trajectories and partner retention. Finally, we would align earlier with central systems and technology to streamline matching, communication, and compensation processes, enabling faster iteration while preserving the program’s developmental and equity-focused design.",
